                          wait {
                            msg ("<br/>I cried like a little baby when I woke up and he gave me a summary of what had happened while I was asleep.<br/><br/>\"You could have pursued your dream of becoming a professional athlete, Loan. You didn't need to take care of me. A burden. I never wanted to be a burden to anyone.<br/><br/>\"And who said that?\"<br/>\"I did.\"<br/>\"Your opinions mean NOTHING to me.\"<br/>\"NOTHING.\"<br/><br/>Asshole. <br/><br/>I love you, Loan. <br/><br/><br/>Thank you.<br/>")
                            wait {
                              msg ("<br/>\"But you could have done it! It could have been your bright future!\"<br/>\"But you are my bright future.\"<br/><br/><br/>I start to shout at him: \"But what if?\"<br/>\"Do you think I would be at peace if I knew I had left you alone? I'm here because I want to be. And I mean it. A future without you will never be a future for me.\"<br/><br/>Why are you smiling? I just shouted at you, why are you smiling? <br/>Why are you being gentle with me?<br/><br/>I don't deserve it.<br/><br/>I deserve to die.<br/><br/>Not you.<br/><br/><br/>Me.<br/><br/><br/>I mean it.")
                              wait {
